definitions.definition: Of or relating to, or forming an orbit (such as the orbit of a moon , planet , or spacecraft ).
Of or relating to the eye socket ( eyehole ) .
Passing around the outside of an urban area.
examples: The M25 is an orbital motorway around London .

main_definition: Of or relating to, or forming an orbit (such as the orbit of a moon , planet , or spacecraft ).
